## Signal Keywords (REQUIRED)

When you complete this iteration, output exactly ONE of the following signals:

- `<aop>TASK_COMPLETE</aop>` - The task is fully complete, all requirements met, tests passing
- `<aop>NEEDS_REVIEW</aop>` - The implementation is ready but needs code review before completion

If you need to continue working (more iterations needed), do NOT output any signal - the workflow will automatically continue with another iteration.

**Important**: Signals must be wrapped in `<aop>` tags exactly as shown above.
